,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"綠帽效應"},{"pid":"b93199d6333f12ae7c7ac3b21d30f4de36fc0633","tid":1809032,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T04:43:28.000Z","msg":"小角色 大事件"},{"pid":"fa25b03bdaeceed5f1364acd4c5bb9a8a38e62b4","tid":1809032,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"自首奇俠"},{"pid":"64202e5db80db2c6aa42ec2f7fb5f5a1607a05d9","tid":1809032,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"神父誘罪"},{"pid":"266d28768be7d5e5ea588a95b7992098c6337af6","tid":1809032,"uid":327209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"4494b9169515459217d25c7781d749ba24b2ff2e","tid":1809032,"uid":49415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9173608dc74b531edd013470566fdb3b68819ebd","tid":1809032,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T19:43:32.000Z","msg":"電影名  故事大綱?有請高人指教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"等候林鄭月娥發落(自首？被自首？司法制度的墮落)<br />\nFrom HKSAR to ROC - The harm of independent jurisdiction<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佳仔在2010年代因為於中華民國臺北市殺人後逃回中華人民共和國香港特別行政區，由於兩地沒有，於香港被逮捕的他只能被判「洗黑錢罪」，可是一直沒有為他的殺人罪名遭司法機關依法處理，不知道何時才可以遭檢控。其後亦於服刑後出獄，他曾透過其代表牧師表示希望赴臺北自首。在2019年年中，香港特區政府主張透過逃犯條例修訂草案來堵塞司法程序的漏洞，但因包括移送疑犯到中國大陸地區，給繼而引發「反送中」抗爭。問題一直拖至2020年代，不知道佳仔何時才能自首..."},{"pid":"e0e2a11f9a59dcfed9b735bdcdd0199d55431782","tid":1809032,"uid":219201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"引渡黑色大痣"},{"pid":"55f2bc3cb16149601f6da84f33f4a567b88bbe7f","tid":1809032,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"香港紙牌屋<br />\n香港風雲"},{"pid":"7d3c15e9c05bbb1e9eb043294e34ef8d47634814","tid":1809032,"uid":216401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:47:51.000Z","msg":"聖誕報佳陰<br />\n應該幾恐怖"},{"pid":"fc66a35a1efb17734c6283be4cd831f4cae92c63","tid":1809032,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶精效應"},{"pid":"2adf950cab953b6c69307756a081ee1152f45e39","tid":1809032,"uid":317874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"佢嗰名叫做陳同佳"}]}